<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>LOL Me / Forget Password</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/lib/bootstrap.min.css"/>
    <link href="/stylesheets/lib/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/dist/custom.css">
</head>
<body class="index-body">

    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="page-img">
            <img src="/images/bg.jpg" alt="bg"/>
        </div>
        <div class="page-container">
            <div class="left-words">
                <h1>欢迎来到 LOL ME。</h1>

                <p>联系你的好友 —和其他吸引你的的用户。获取你感兴趣的事情的实时更新。并透过全方位直播见证事件在你的眼前展开。</p>

                <div class="author-info">
                    <p>本网站由nicholas开发完成，主要目的是希望在大家忙碌辛苦的生活中，增添一点乐趣，每天都能开怀一笑！</p>

                    <p id="contact-me">联系我?</p>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li><a href="mailto:yitaqi2011@gmail.com?Subject=From Lolme user"><i class="fa fa-envelope-o"></i> yitaqi2011@gmail.com</a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://twitter.com/Normal_Geek_Xue"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i> twitter@Normal_Geek_Xue</a></li>
                        <li><a data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal" style="cursor: pointer;"><i class="fa fa-weixin"></i> 微信</a></li>
                        <li><a href="http://weibo.com/u/1664314377"><i class="fa fa-weibo"></i> 微博@Nicholas__Xue</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sign-wrap" id="signin-wrap">
                <form action="/forget-pass" method="post">
                    <div class="form-group signin-title">
                        <h1>忘记密码</h1>
                    </div>
                    <% if (locals.error) { %>
                        <div class="alert alert-warning">
                            <strong><%= locals.error %></strong>
                        </div>
                    <% } %>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="email" placeholder="输入你注册时所用邮箱" required>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm btn-info">确定</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog" style="width: 330px;">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span><span class="sr-only">Close</span></button>
            <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">We Chat</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body">
              <img src="/images/wechat-qrcode.png"
              class="img-responsive img-rounded"
              alt="we chat qrcode"
              width="300" height="300">
          </div>
          <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

<!-- jQuery文件。务必在bootstrap.min.js 之前引入 -->
<script src="/javascripts/lib/jquery-1.11.1.min.js"></script>
<!-- 最新的 Bootstrap 核心 JavaScript 文件 -->
<script src="/javascripts/lib/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>